  ($$Bach to Baby Family Concert, Pimlico$$, $$St Gabriel's Church, Warwick Square, Victoria & Pimlico, SW1V 2AD$$, $$SW1V 2AD$$, 51.489994, -0.1427125, $$Music & singing$$, $$15:00$$, $$15:45$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=St%20Gabriel's%20Church%2C%20Warwick%20Square%2C%20Victoria%20%26%20Pimlico%2C%20SW1V%202AD$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/bach-to-baby/bach-to-baby-family-concert-pimlico/29616$$, $$https://bachtobaby.com/$$, 5, null, 0, $$Suitable for: 1, 2, 3, 4, 0-6m, 6-12m$$, $$London$$, '{}', $$Times and availability sourced from Loopla. Check Loopla before travelling.$$, $$Bach to Baby is the critically acclaimed concert series for babies, toddlers and their carers. Tots dance, roam about and revel in the wonder of live music, while you take a moment out of your busy day to hear top notch performances by outstanding musicians, with your young babes in tow. Outstanding Musicians, Exhilarating Performances, Inspiring Locations across the UK. As seen at Royal Albert Hall and Buckingham Palace. Featured in The Times (London) and the New York Times. Extra Information Remember: Up to 2 children come free on every Adult Ticket! Doors open 15 minutes before, and concerts last for about 45 minutes.$$, $$GBP 16.00 from Loopla$$, true, $$Loopla London events and activities$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/bach-to-baby/bach-to-baby-family-concert-pimlico/29616$$, $$https://loopla-prod-images.loopla.com/cdn-cgi/image/w=1000,f=auto/a227b3c235bc/7907eb3edcf2aa9f529e40fca451d2b967af59e3.png$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/bach-to-baby/bach-to-baby-family-concert-pimlico/29616$$, $$other$$, $$2026-08-16$$, array[$$2026-08-16$$]::date[], null, null, '{}', $$one_off$$, $$Loopla lists this activity on 2026-08-16.$$, $$published$$),
  ($$Bach to Baby Half Term Concert, Notting Hill$$, $$St Peter's Church, Kensington Park Road, Notting Hill, W11 2PN$$, $$W11 2PN$$, 51.5127335, -0.2030284, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:30$$, $$11:15$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=St%20Peter's%20Church%2C%20Kensington%20Park%20Road%2C%20Notting%20Hill%2C%20W11%202PN$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/bach-to-baby/bach-to-baby-half-term-concert-notting-hill/29601$$, $$https://bachtobaby.com/$$, 5, null, 0, $$Suitable for: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 0-6m, 6-12m$$, $$London$$, '{}', $$Times and availability sourced from Loopla. Check Loopla before travelling.$$, $$Come and join Bach to Baby this Half Term for a specially designed programme of classical music for the whole family to enjoy together. About Bach to Baby Bach to Baby is the critically acclaimed concert series for babies, toddlers and their carers. Tots dance, roam about and revel in the wonder of live music, while you take a moment out of your busy day to hear top notch performances by outstanding musicians, with your young babes in tow. Outstanding Musicians, Exhilarating Performances, Inspiring Locations across the UK. As seen at Royal Albert Hall and Buckingham Palace. Featured in The Times (London) and the New York Times. Extra Information Remember: Up to 2 children come free on every Adult Ticket! Doors open 15 minutes before, and concerts last for about 45 minutes.$$, $$GBP 16.00 from Loopla$$, true, $$Loopla London events and activities$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/bach-to-baby/bach-to-baby-half-term-concert-notting-hill/29601$$, $$https://loopla-prod-images.loopla.com/cdn-cgi/image/w=1000,f=auto/a227b3c235bc/d804dd1ac4c5d525bdf0f93927433615c05d8ed9.png$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/bach-to-baby/bach-to-baby-half-term-concert-notting-hill/29601$$, $$other$$, $$2026-10-26$$, array[$$2026-10-26$$]::date[], null, null, '{}', $$one_off$$, $$Loopla lists this activity on 2026-10-26.$$, $$published$$),
  ($$Be Like Blippi$$, $$The Arts at Marble Arch, Marble Arch, W1H 7DX$$, $$W1H 7DX$$, 51.5188408, -0.1601099, $$Family activities$$, $$10:00$$, $$11:30$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=The%20Arts%20at%20Marble%20Arch%2C%20Marble%20Arch%2C%20W1H%207DX$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/the-arts-at-march-arch/be-like-blippi/31506$$, null, 5, null, 0, $$Suitable for: 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7$$, $$London$$, '{}', $$Times and availability sourced from Loopla. Check Loopla before travelling.$$, $$Get ready to see the world more curiously, because Blippi is coming to The Arts at Marble Arch in the all-new BE LIKE BLIPPI Tour! Join Blippi and Meekah live on stage for a one-of-a-kind interactive adventure that inspires kids to move like, play like, and explore just like Blippi! This brand-new show is packed with high-energy music and surprises, featuring fan-favorite songs like “The Excavator Song,” “Monster Truck,” “Dino Dance,” and “Curious Like Me.” With Blippi’s signature mix of play, learning, and exploration, families can get curious together while singing, laughing, and dancing along during this unforgettable adventure full of fun and discovery. For the BE LIKE BLIPPI Tour, the characters Blippi and Meekah will be played by professional stage performers selected specifically for the tour. What is BE LIKE BLIPPI about? The Be Like Blippi Tour invites you to break out your orange Blippi glasses and ignite that spark of curiosity that lives inside every single one of us and share in an unforgettable experience that encourages kids to… Be Like Blippi! About The Arts at Marble Arch Louis Hartshorn and Brian Hook are delighted to announce the Arts Theatre's new temporary home$$, $$GBP 24.00 from Loopla$$, true, $$Loopla London events and activities$$, $$https://loopla.com/business/the-arts-at-march-arch/be-like-blippi/31506$$, $$https://loopla-prod-images.loopla.com/cdn-cgi/image/w=1000,f=auto/e2cc52458081/5630dc70f77c3e25399d0132c25fb1bc7eb73ce8.png$$, $$https:/